text.section:
The department shall organize the selection committee's first meeting. At that meeting, the selection committee shall:
Elect from its members a chairman and a vice chairman who shall hold their positions for the duration of the selection process;
Be provided with:
The certified list of firms;
The firms' written proposals submitted in response to a request for proposals;
The request for proposals;
The notice of request for proposals;
The proposal evaluation sheets; and
A notice from the commissioner informing the committee that the selection process is governed by KRS 56.800 to 56.823 and 56.990; and
Discuss the future conduct of its affairs.
